    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em>You loudly proclaim that fate is on your side, or that fate has something terrible in store for your enemies. You smash a glass object or strike a bell, and the sound reverberates through the air. Your enemies feel a sense of dread as your words are punctuated with magic worming through their minds.</em></p><p><strong>Charisma</strong> <strong>Save</strong> </p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 2d6 psychic]] damage*. If target isn't immune to &amp;reference[psychic] damage, they have disadvantage on the next attack roll or skill check they make.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage, no other effect.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*</strong> <strong>Upcasting:</strong> Increase damage by [[/damage 1d6 psychic]]{1d6} for each spell level above 3rd.</p>",
            "chat": "<strong>Charisma</strong> <strong>Save</strong> </p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 2d6 psychic]] damage*. If target isn't immune to &amp;reference[psychic] damage, they have disadvantage on the next attack roll or skill check they make.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage, no other effect.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*</strong> <strong>Upcasting</strong> : Increase damage by [[/damage 1d6 psychic]]{1d6} for each spell level above 3rd.</p>"
